@niche: I think she only realized it halfway through, but once she did, thats why she gave him permission to "do it raw" as a special exception.
Kiasa has a thing for doing a lot of NTR from the girl's side of things rather than having the girl be stolen, she does the stealing. This was sort of a mix of both, I feel like this should have a netori tag.
@Zero_35: yeah, "friend" was a major douche bag, but he technically didn't do anything wrong either. If anything, in the end I think she decided to give herself for real to our "main" protagonist.
